Barry WILLIAMS, Appellant-Petitioner,
v.
DEPARTMENT OF CORRECTIONS, Respondent-Respondent. C-491 September Term 2017
078864 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 12, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005401-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
